    <item>
      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，台积电和三星考虑在阿联酋新建大型芯片工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/tsmc-samsung-weigh-major-new-chip-factories-in-uae-wsj-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》报道，随着人工智能的兴起，台湾半导体制造公司和三星电子公司已讨论未来几年在阿联酋建设大型新工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/tsmc-samsung-weigh-major-new-chip-factories-in-uae-wsj-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 18:10:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉寻求在巴西 G20 峰会期间带头推动全球人工智能规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/lula-seeks-to-lead-push-for-global-ai-rules-during-brazil-s-g-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当全球最大的几个经济体难以就人工智能的未来达成共识时，巴西的路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦希望确保发展中国家不会被排除在辩论之外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/lula-seeks-to-lead-push-for-global-ai-rules-during-brazil-s-g-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 14:13:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果新款 iPhone 16 反映出创新步伐放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-09-22/apple-iphone-16-pro-max-review-new-model-reflects-slowing-pace-of-innovation-m1dkn8jv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新款 iPhone 的摄像头功能有了显著改进，但这款设备象征着苹果硬件创新步伐的放缓。此外：该公司正准备在明年对 iOS 18 进行一系列更新；一款令人眼花缭乱的全新 Apple Watch 配置仍未确定；iOS 18.1 的最新测试版已经发布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-09-22/apple-iphone-16-pro-max-review-new-model-reflects-slowing-pace-of-innovation-m1dkn8jv</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 12:45:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利电信和 Asterion 将收购意大利电信旗下 Sparkle 子公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/italy-asterion-to-make-offer-for-telecom-italia-s-sparkle-unit-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《共和报》报道，意大利正准备与西班牙投资公司 Asterion Industrial Partners 组成财团，竞购意大利电信 (Telecom Italia SpA) 旗下海底电缆部门 Sparkle。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/italy-asterion-to-make-offer-for-telecom-italia-s-sparkle-unit-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 10:41:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度政府寻求对亚马逊和 Flipkart 财务部门处以罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/india-seeks-amazon-flipkart-financials-for-penalty-mint-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Mint 援引两位知情人士透露，印度竞争委员会要求亚马逊卖家服务和 Flipkart Internet 分享财务报表，以确定正在进行的反垄断案件中可能受到的处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/india-seeks-amazon-flipkart-financials-for-penalty-mint-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:20:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vodafone Idea 与诺基亚、三星签署 36 亿美元网络协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/vodafone-idea-inks-3-6-billion-network-deal-with-nokia-samsung</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Vodafone Idea 有限公司已与诺基亚公司等公司签署了一份价值 36 亿美元的合同，为这家印度电话运营商提供设备，用于其网络的计划升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/vodafone-idea-inks-3-6-billion-network-deal-with-nokia-samsung</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:09:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登政府准备禁止中国汽车软件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/biden-administration-to-prepare-ban-on-chinese-car-software</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国商务部计划最早于周一公布禁止中国和俄罗斯制造的车联网硬件和软件的拟议规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/biden-administration-to-prepare-ban-on-chinese-car-software</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 22:34:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
