    <item>
      <title>谷歌广告辩护开始，法官质疑公司证词</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/google-judge-questions-company-testimony-as-ad-defense-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谷歌一位高管试图反驳美国司法部针对其展示广告技术业务的反垄断案，并作证称，谷歌面临来自微软公司、亚马逊公司和 Meta Platforms 公司等公司的“激烈竞争”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/google-judge-questions-company-testimony-as-ad-defense-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 23:16:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rocket Lab 卫星发射让 SpaceX Challenger 重回正轨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/rocket-lab-satellite-launch-puts-spacex-challenger-back-on-track</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rocket Lab USA Inc. 发射了小型卫星电子火箭，使该公司在最后的倒计时中止了之前的尝试后重回正轨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/rocket-lab-satellite-launch-puts-spacex-challenger-back-on-track</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 23:08:02 GMT</pubDate>
